<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Blog – Jackstar’s Journal</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Read articles, guides, and opinions from Jackstar on web development, design, and technology.">
    <meta name="author" content="Jackstar">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/root.css') }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/navbar.css') }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/footer.css') }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/blog.css') }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-pb1a8fR2IG23QMGYBk8zQ7C0r4kOG55G4+7RThd7GxVbxmYFZHzqLTXW2dEVxErbqD0kKcl00Kd6cTDyXv4qOQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="" type="image">
</head>
<body>
    {% include "snippets/navbar.jinja-html" %}

    <main class="blog-container container">
    <header class="blog-minimal-header">
        <div class="section-label">Journal</div>
        <h1>Articles & Perspectives</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="blog-toolbar">
        <div class="search-wrapper">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Search articles...">
        </div>
        
        <button class="filter-toggle-btn" id="filter-btn">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-sliders"></i>
            <span>Filters</span>
        </button>
    </section>

    <section class="filter-drawer" id="filter-drawer">
        <div class="drawer-inner">
            <div class="filter-col filter-group">
                <label><i class="fa-solid fa-sort"></i> Sort</label>
                <div class="filter-select-wrapper">
                    <select>
                        <option value="newest">🔽 Newest</option>
                        <option value="oldest">🔼 Oldest</option>
                    </select>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down dropdown-icon"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="filter-col filter-group">
                <label><i class="fa-solid fa-folder-open"></i> Topics</label>
                <div class="filter-select-wrapper">
                    <select>
                        <option>All Topics</option>
                        <option>Engineering</option>
                        <option>Design</option>
                        <option>Ecosystem</option>
                        <option>Tools</option>
                    </select>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down dropdown-icon"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="filter-col filter-group">
                <label><i class="fa-solid fa-tags"></i> Tags</label>
                <div class="tag-input">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="e.g. Python, UI Design">
                    <div class="tag-suggestions">
                        <span>#Python</span>
                        <span>#AI</span>
                        <span>#UI-Design</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="filter-col filter-group">
                <label><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i> Date</label>
                <div class="filter-date-range">
                    <input type="date"><span>to</span><input type="date">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="filter-col filter-group filter-collapsible">
                <input type="checkbox" id="reading-time-toggle" class="filter-toggle-checkbox">
                <label for="reading-time-toggle" class="filter-label-collapsible"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i> Reading Time <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i></label>
                <div class="filter-list-group">
                    <label class="filter-list-item">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-rabbit"></i>
                        <span>Short (&lt;5 min)</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="filter-list-item">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-person-hiking"></i>
                        <span>Medium (5‑15 min)</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="filter-list-item">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-book"></i>
                        <span>Deep Dive (&gt;15 min)</span>
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="filter-col filter-group filter-collapsible">
                <input type="checkbox" id="type-toggle" class="filter-toggle-checkbox">
                <label for="type-toggle" class="filter-label-collapsible"><i class="fa-solid fa-list"></i> Type <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i></label>
                <div class="filter-list-group">
                    <label class="filter-list-item">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i>
                        <span>Guide</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="filter-list-item">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-pen-fancy"></i>
                        <span>Opinion</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="filter-list-item">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-microphone"></i>
                        <span>Interview</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="filter-list-item">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-newspaper"></i>
                        <span>News</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="filter-list-item">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                        <span>Review</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="filter-list-item">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-gear"></i>
                        <span>Meta</span>
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="clear-filters-btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-rotate-left"></i> Clear All</button>
    </section>

    <section class="blog-list">
        <article class="blog-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Post Cover">
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <div class="card-meta">
                    <span class="tag">Engineering</span>
                    <span class="dot">•</span>
                    <span class="date">March 12, 2026</span>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="card-title">
                    <h2>Advanced State Management</h2>
                </a>
                <div class="title-divider"></div>
                <p>Exploring how to handle complex data flows in modern web applications without sacrificing performance or scalability.</p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558655146-d09347e92766?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="UI Design">
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <div class="card-meta">
                    <span class="tag">Design</span>
                    <span class="dot">•</span>
                    <span class="date">March 5, 2026</span>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="card-title">
                    <h2>The Future of Minimalist Interfaces</h2>
                </a>
                <div class="title-divider"></div>
                <p>Why "less is more" is evolving into "less is better." A deep dive into the psychological impact of reduced UI clutter.</p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="blog-card-v2">
            <div class="card-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517077304055-6e89abbf09b0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Tech in Austria">
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <div class="card-meta">
                    <span class="tag">Ecosystem</span>
                    <span class="dot">•</span>
                    <span class="date">February 28, 2026</span>
                </div>
                <a href="#" class="card-title">
                    <h2>Vienna's Growing Tech Scene</h2>
                </a>
                <div class="title-divider"></div>
                <p>Highlighting the innovative startups making waves in Austria and how the local landscape is shifting toward AI-driven solutions.</p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <div class="blog-load-more">
            <button class="btn-load-more"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down"></i> Load More Articles</button>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
    {% include "snippets/footer.jinja-html" %}
    <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/global.js') }}"></script>
</body>
</html>